info.author: Imran Geriskovan
info.description:
TreePyO enables visual navigation of full object hierarcy within a Python runtime. It is ideal for grasping internals of an object_group/application. Objects, members, classes, functions, modules, lists, dicts, etc; namely, any object hierarcy can be navigated as they are alive. Screenshot:
https://github.com/imrn/TreePyO/blob/master/treepyo.jpg
info.keywords: Object Hierarcy Tree Navigator Browser GObject Introspection GTK
info.name: TreePyO
info.summary: Object Hierarcy Tree Navigator for Python
